From: SeongJae Park <sj@kernel.org>
Date: Tue, 10 Feb 2026 21:51:11 -0800
Subject: [PATCH] ==== deprecate core_filters sysfs dir ====

mm/damon/sysfs: document filters/ directory as deprecated

Now core_filters/ and ops_filters/ are well stabilized.  Existence of
filters/ directory is only confusing.

We will make yearly deprecation step, similar to those for DAMON debugfs
deprecation.

This change mark it deprecated with a note of alternatives.

In 2027, we will add warning on use of filters/ directory.
In 2028, we will rename filters/ directory to filters_DEPRECATED/.
In 2029, we will remove filters_DEPRECATED/ directory.

Signed-off-by: SeongJae Park <sj@kernel.org>
---
 hkml_cv_bogus/hkml_cv_bogus_to9qsvb4 | 0
 1 file changed, 0 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)
